    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This unit delivers linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline, facilitated by its six individual throttle bodies. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission offers precise engagement, paired with a factory M Variable Differential Lock for optimal corner-exit traction. Significant preventative maintenance has been performed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The suspension retains its factory-tuned damping characteristics, providing a communicative feedback loop through the hydraulic rack-and-pinion steering. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its well-maintained status, the powertrain remains tight and the throttle response is razor-sharp. A definitive driver\u2019s specimen for the purist who prioritizes mechanical integrity.",
